    { "id": "sres-t", "type": "text", "x": 1038, "y": 333, "width": 298, "height": 60, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#495057", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 60021, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 60021, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "🧱 reserved ≈ 8 cores  (¼)\nOS · k8s · KEDA · redis\napi · workers · sidecars", "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "sres", "originalText": "🧱 reserved ≈ 8 cores  (¼)\nOS · k8s · KEDA · redis\napi · workers · sidecars", "lineHeight": 1.25 },

    { "id": "barCap", "type": "text", "x": 60, "y": 420, "width": 1288, "height": 18, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#868e96", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 60022, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 60022, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "Σ inference = 2×8 + 2×4 = 24 cores  ·  leaves ~8 (¼ of the box) free   |   KEDA ceilings stay per-model (32B max 3, 8B max 4) — the scheduler caps the global sum", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "containerId": null, "originalText": "Σ inference = 2×8 + 2×4 = 24 cores  ·  leaves ~8 (¼ of the box) free   |   KEDA ceilings stay per-model (32B max 3, 8B max 4) — the scheduler caps the global sum", "lineHeight": 1.25 },

    { "id": "ramT", "type": "rectangle", "x": 60, "y": 470, "width": 560, "height": 150, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#2f9e44", "backgroundColor": "#ebfbee", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 60023, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 60023, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "ramT-t"}], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false },
    { "id": "ramT-t", "type": "text", "x": 80, "y": 490, "width": 520, "height": 110, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#2b8a3e", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 60024, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 60024, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "🧮 RAM check (the easy ceiling)\nweights:  2×24 + 2×8  = 64 GB\n+ KV cache (ctx 8192)  ≈ 16 GB\n≈ 80 GB of 128  ✓   (~48 GB headroom)", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "ramT", "originalText": "🧮 RAM check (the easy ceiling)\nweights:  2×24 + 2×8  = 64 GB\n+ KV cache (ctx 8192)  ≈ 16 GB\n≈ 80 GB of 128  ✓   (~48 GB headroom)", "lineHeight": 1.4 },

    { "id": "enf", "type": "rectangle", "x": 660, "y": 470, "width": 688, "height": 150, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#e03131", "backgroundColor": "#fff0f0", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": {"type": 3}, "seed": 60025, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 60025, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [{"type": "text", "id": "enf-t"}], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false },
    { "id": "enf-t", "type": "text", "x": 680, "y": 484, "width": 648, "height": 122, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#c92a2a", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "strokeStyle": "solid", "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "groupIds": [], "frameId": null, "roundness": null, "seed": 60026, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 60026, "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": [], "updated": 1, "link": null, "locked": false, "fontSize": 13, "fontFamily": 2, "text": "⚖️ How the budget is ENFORCED — config/models.json\nINVARIANT:  llm_args.threads  ==  resources.llm.requests.cpu\n→ the k8s scheduler reserves exactly the cores a pod will burn\n→ overflow KEDA replicas (3×8 + 4×4 = 40 > 32) stay Pending,\n    they never oversubscribe / thrash CPU\nset this round:  32B threads 16→8 (lim 16→10) · 8B threads 8→4 (lim 8→5)", "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle", "containerId": "enf", "originalText": "⚖️ How the budget is ENFORCED — config/models.json\nINVARIANT:  llm_args.threads  ==  resources.llm.requests.cpu\n→ the k8s scheduler reserves exactly the cores a pod will burn\n→ overflow KEDA replicas (3×8 + 4×4 = 40 > 32) stay Pending,\n    they never oversubscribe / thrash CPU\nset this round:  32B threads 16→8 (lim 16→10) · 8B threads 8→4 (lim 8→5)", "lineHeight": 1.35 },

